projects.name: GenAI Acceleration Hub
projects.description:
GenAI Acceleration Hub – Project Overview (EN)

Section
Summary
Mission
Accelerate enterprises’ journey from GenAI curiosity to measurable business value in ≤ 12 months.
Core Offerings
1. Discovery Workshops – opportunity mapping & ROI framing2. Pilot Factory – 4- to 6-week PoCs using clients’ data & workflows3. Enablement Tracks – role-based up-skilling (exec, product, tech)4. Governance Framework – risk, compliance, and model lifecycle guidance5. Scaled Deployment Support – MLOps, change-management, KPI dashboards
Engagement Model
Modular packages (Explore → Pilot → Scale) with clear exit criteria; blended on-site / remote team; success fees tied to KPI attainment.
Target Industries
Manufacturing, real-estate/services, retail, logistics, finance – prioritised by data maturity & generative-content needs.
Success Metrics
• 3+ productionized GenAI use-cases per client • ≥ 20 % reduction in manual knowledge-work hours • NPS ≥ 60
Key Differentiators
⚡ End-to-end capabilities (strategy-to-MLOps)
